<concept id="conceptId">
    <title>About PCC/PVC</title>
    <conbody>
        <p><i>Phon</i> has the ability to calculate the percentage of attempted consonants or vowels
            which are produced correctly (<i>Percent Consonants Correct</i>/<i>Percent Vowels
                Correct</i>).</p>
        <p>The number returned from a PCC or PVC calculation will be in the following format:</p>
        <p>&lt;# correct>/&lt;# attempted>;&lt;# deleted>;&lt;# epenthesized></p>
        
